    <user>anag_factory</user>
    <comment>- update to 1.1.0:
  * Generalize loo expectations
  * Add std, var, iqr and mad
  * Set histogram density=True by default
  * Add method to compute influential observations based on
    leave-one-out expectations
  * Add custom log-likelihood to `loo()`
  * Add new uniformity test
  * Fix mcse for circular variables
  * Make elpd_diff negative
  * Remove long docstring examples
  * Remove `khat` display in example docstring
  * Fix compare() docstring, return object column name now
    matches docstring
  * Update `compare()` docstring
  * Enhance method descriptions for R-hat computation
  * Document kwargs for kde across all layers</comment>
    <requestid>1349363</requestid>
  </revision>
  <revision rev="3" vrev="1">
