    <user>anag_factory</user>
    <comment>- update to 1.2.0:
  * Return shapley values in original order
  * scale ISJ bw estimate by grid range rather than data range
  * Add kde2d functions
  * Generalize and refactor bayes_factor
  * Add p_worse, diff and elpd diagnostics to compare
  * prepare release</comment>
